						<summary>

						<p>This mutilated record refers itself to <hi rend="bold">Traiḷōkyamalladēva.</hi> From the alphabet it may be assigned to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Trailōkyamalla Sōmēśvara I.</hi> The stone is broken after the mention of the king's name and no further details are available.</p>						

